- Where were you all summer?
- Are you my mother?

72
00:05:30.529 --> 00:05:33.945
- Just askin'.
- Working. More than you can say.

73
00:05:34.074 --> 00:05:37.492
- Working?
- Yes. lugging boxes at Bargain City.

74
00:05:37.621 --> 00:05:39.993
- Nice job.
- Eat me.

75
