82
00:06:11.119 --> 00:06:13.788
I was hanging around at the beach.
You know.

83
00:06:13.914 --> 00:06:16.831
It's tough with all those chicks
hanging around you.

84
00:06:16.958 --> 00:06:21.004
The only thing
that hangs around you are the flies.

85
00:06:21.130 --> 00:06:24.168
How was the action
at the beach. man?

86
00:06:24.468 --> 00:06:26.793
Whew. It was flipping.

87
00:06:26.928 --> 00:06:28.673
Yeah? Crazy?

88
00:06:28.806 --> 00:06:33.184
I did meet this one chick.
She was sorta cool.

89
00:06:33.311 --> 00:06:35.470
You mean she puts out?

90
