149
00:10:18.745 --> 00:10:22.448
Good morning. boys and girls.
Welcome to what we're sure will be

150
00:10:22.584 --> 00:10:24.707
our greatest year at Rydell. 

151
00:10:24.836 --> 00:10:28.253
Saturday night will be
our first pep rally and bonfire. 

152
00:10:28.382 --> 00:10:30.955
I want to see all of you students
out there. 

153
00:10:31.093 --> 00:10:35.841
with plenty of support for Coach
Calhoun and the Rydell Rangers. 

154
00:10:35.975 --> 00:10:40.139
If you can't be an athlete.
be an athletic supporter.

155
00:10:40.772 --> 00:10:43.097
And now for the really good news. 

156
00:10:43.232 --> 00:10:45.226
One of the most exciting things

157
00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:48.066
to ever happen at Rydell High.

158
00:10:48.198 --> 00:10:50.984
National Bandstand television show

159
00:10:51.117 --> 00:10:55.580
has selected Rydell as
a representative American high school

160
00:10:55.707 --> 00:10:59.325
and will do a live broadcast
from our very own gym.

161
00:10:59.460 --> 00:11:01.086
(cheering)

162
00:11:01.213 --> 00:11:04.048
It is our chance
to show the entire nation

163
00:11:04.174 --> 00:11:06.845
what fine. bright. clean-cut.

164
00:11:06.970 --> 00:11:11.098
wholesome students
we have here at Rydell.

