178
00:11:59.866 --> 00:12:02.867
Yeah. just for school.
Do they make me look smarter?

179
00:12:02.994 --> 00:12:05.153
Nah. you can still see your face.

180
00:12:05.289 --> 00:12:08.788
- How d'you like school. Sandy?
- It's different.

181
00:12:08.917 --> 00:12:11.410
