Patty Simcox.
the bad seed of Rydell. Hi.

183
00:12:14.425 --> 00:12:17.794
- I love the first day of school.
- The biggest thrill of my life.

184
00:12:17.928 --> 00:12:20.634
- You won't guess what's happened.
- Probably not.

185
00:12:20.766 --> 00:12:22.924
The nominees for Student Council
are out.

186
00:12:23.059 --> 00:12:25.349
- Guess who's up for Vice President?
- Who?

187
00:12:25.479 --> 00:12:27.223
Me. Isn't that the most?

188
00:12:27.357 --> 00:12:29.349
- To say the least.
- The very least.

189
00:12:29.484 --> 00:12:31.442
I hope I don't make a poor showing.

190
00:12:31.570 --> 00:12:34.441
We wish you the best of luck.
don't we. girls?

191
00:12:34.574 --> 00:12:36.317
I've got my fingers crossed.

192
00:12:37.493 --> 00:12:41.327
Oh. you must think I'm a clod
for not introducing myself.

193
00:12:41.457 --> 00:12:43.829
Hi. I'm Patty Simcox.

194
00:12:44.001 --> 00:12:46.125
Welcome to Rydell. (squeals)

195
00:12:50.759 --> 00:12:54.923
Will you be at cheerleader tryouts?
We'll be lifelong friends.

196
00:12:55.055 --> 00:12:57.595
You guys. how do you like Sandy?

197
00:12:57.726 --> 00:13:00.300
Do you think we can
let her in the Pink Ladies?

198
00:13:01.605 --> 00:13:04.975
- She looks too pure to be pink.
- Ohh. double do-do!

199
00:13:05.109 --> 00:13:06.224
What's up. doc?

200
00:13:06.361 --> 00:13:09.066
One of my diamonds
just fell in the macaroni.

201
00:13:10.783 --> 00:13:13.026
Kenickie. want a piece of salami?

202
00:13:13.161 --> 00:13:15.782
Are you kidding?
If I eat that. I'll smell like you.

203
00:13:15.914 --> 00:13:17.539
What a stink!

204
00:13:17.666 --> 00:13:19.244
Hey. guys. look.

205
00:13:21.129 --> 00:13:24.581
Ladies and gentlemen.
dingleberries on parade.

206
00:13:26.469 --> 00:13:30.052
Look! You really put
your foot into it this time.

207
00:13:30.181 --> 00:13:32.755
Try hopscotch. you hot dog.

208
00:13:33.727 --> 00:13:36.728
What a gavone! Gumdrops. man.

209
00:13:40.193 --> 00:13:43.396
Any of you guys see
that new chick in registration?

210
00:13:43.530 --> 00:13:45.607
Sure beats
the foam domes round here.

211
00:13:45.741 --> 00:13:47.367
Jugs bigger than Annette's?

212
00:13:47.494 --> 00:13:50.780
Nobody's jugs
are bigger than Annette's.

213
00:13:55.627 --> 00:13:57.751
Hey. guys. Hey!

214
00:14:01.050 --> 00:14:02.676
Hi. girls.

215
00:14:03.137 --> 00:14:04.964
You're a sick man. Putz.

216
00:14:08.351 --> 00:14:11.437
Hey. I wanna hear about
what Danny did at the beach.

217
00:14:12.106 --> 00:14:15.605
- It was nothing.
- Sure. nothing. Zuko. Right?

218
00:14:15.735 --> 00:14:18.820
- You got in her drawers. right?
- Come on. tell us.

219
00:14:18.947 --> 00:14:20.407
