220
00:14:20.533 --> 00:14:23.819
I spent most of it at the beach.
I met a boy there.

221
00:14:23.953 --> 00:14:26.658
You hauled your cookies
to the beach for a guy?

222
00:14:26.791 --> 00:14:30.160
- He was sorta special.
- There ain't no such thing.

223
00:14:31.504 --> 00:14:32.963
It was really romantic.

224
00:14:33.089 --> 00:14:35.414
Everything about it.

225
00:14:35.550 --> 00:14:38.468
